cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.DS 

This paper deals with image processing and specifically focuses on detecting double JPEG compression. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). As the paper deals with image forgery detection, it could also belong to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves data analysis and feature reduction, which could fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
